Package: getMODIS
Type: Package
Title: keaping a used-defined MODIS ftp 'mirror' and pre-processing of MODIS grid data   
Version: 0.1
Date: 2011-08-10
Depends: RCurl
Suggests: audio
Author: Matteo Mattiuzzi
Maintainer: Matteo Mattiuzzi <matteo@mattiuzzi.com>
Description: User can define which MODIS data to download. Which in the sense of MODIS-PRODUCT and VERSION, AREA, PERIOD. The functions here are doing the rest by creating a userdefined subset of the online MODIS-grid archive (ftp://e4ftl01u.ecs.nasa.gov/). Installing some additional software it is possible to further process downloaded data with all their capabilities
 - MODIS ReprojectionTool (MRT): https://lpdaac.usgs.gov/lpdaac/tools/modis_reprojection_tool
 - LDOPE: https://lpdaac.usgs.gov/lpdaac/tools/ldope_tools
only Windows:
 - dos2unix ()
License: GPL (>=3)
LazyLoad: yes
